  "wechat_html": "<section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:28px 14px 40px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.18);box-shadow:0 18px 48px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);border-radius:28px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:28px 24px 18px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:34px;line-height:1.25;margin:16px 0 14px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">3月12日：历史上的今天</h1><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.9;color:#475569;margin:0 0 4px;\">回顾历史，见证全球重要纪念日与古迹重建。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 24px 28px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.9);border-radius:22px;padding:20px 18px;margin:0 0 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历史的长河中，3月12日承载着多样的纪念意义。这一天被定为世界反网络审查日，旨在唤起全球对数字空间自由与开放的关注，提醒人们在互联网时代保护信息获取权利的重要性。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 22px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:22px;display:block;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.9);border-radius:22px;padding:20px 18px;margin:0 0 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin:0;color:#334155;\">将视线投向遥远的印度洋，模里西斯在这一天庆祝其独立日。作为一个由多岛屿组成的国家，模里西斯以其独特的地理位置和丰富的文化底蕴，在这一天共同欢庆民族独立的辉煌时刻。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 22px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:22px;display:block;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.9);border-radius:22px;padding:20px 18px;margin:0 0 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin:0;color:#334155;\">时光倒流至公元前515年，人类文明史册上记录了一项宏伟的工程。在波斯帝国国王大流士一世的支持下，耶路撒冷圣殿得以重建，这一历史事件标志着当地信仰中心的重要复兴。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 22px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:22px;display:block;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.9);border-radius:22px;padding:20px 18px;margin:0 0 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin:0;color:#334155;\">这些历史与纪念日不仅是时间的节点，更是人类社会不断演进与追求发展的缩影。从古代建筑的修复到现代数字权利的倡议，每一个事件都折射出不同时代背景下的社会诉求。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 22px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:22px;display:block;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.9);border-radius:22px;padding:20px 18px;margin:0 0 18px;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);\"><p style=\"font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin:0;color:#334155;\">通过回顾这些历史碎片，我们能够更好地理解世界的多元性。无论是在古老的遗迹中寻找文明的足迹，还是在现代议题中探讨自由的边界，3月12日都为我们提供了独特的观察视角。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 22px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-12/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:22px;display:block;box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);\"></div></section></section></section></section>"
